{"tid":2310590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢炎好恐怖? 今日又一單有老野唔驗唔知中左仲已經有抗體 即係代表咩","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T04:07:03.000Z","uid":78016,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ad0737c535a3906715527e043da464dd177089","tid":2310590,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"廢炎係垃圾囉 屌你老味<br />\n又一單唔驗唔知中左 無後遺症 已康復 藥都唔洗食 82歲都唔驚<br />\n明明弱感冒黎 驚到春咁 <br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎．最新｜增90宗確診31宗無源頭　御滿屋廚師中招須停業<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/556818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F556818&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=2db9dcf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/556818</a><br />\n<br />\n【17:26】劉家獻重申，該名82歲瑪嘉烈醫院女病人，在昨日驗抗體呈陽性，即代表她已康復，傳染性不高，但她體內何時有抗體仍要繼續調查。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾恐懼撚精神病人 返屋企縮返入你老母個西度啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b98469e3b28c04bbd7f138ed22eef481219c92f","tid":2310590,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5ef38b88040be336089e9f57a62c5946bf9153","tid":2310590,"uid":31237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"唔中唔知身體好"},{"pid":"d065d572c4327f8172ff685459afe2727ca9573e","tid":2310590,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"威 又可以瘋狂叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab196e24b33a97a903dea9c92caf7ef293ff37f8","tid":2310590,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/